>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">EASY TO USE AT HOME: The razor comb can shorten and shape both thin and thick hair. If you have thin hair, use the fine teeth side. If you have thick hair, use the wide teeth side</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DOUBLE-SIDED HAIR CUTTING COMB: Hair comb on one end and the double sided razor comb for thinning hair and trimming on the other. For use on all hair including facial hair</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">UNWANTED FACIAL HAIR: Ideal for quickly removing unwanted hair without the hassles of shaving. Can be used for men and women, beads, mustaches, and all facial hair</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SAFELY CUTS HAIR: Shorten, shape, and thin your hair. The safety shielded razor protects from cutting or scratching your skin. (4) Cutting Lengths: Extra Short Hair, Short Hair, Medium Hair, Light Hair</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">REUSABLE WITH INCLUDED BONUS BLADES: Includes (5) replacement blades included. Uses standard double sided razor blades. Life of blades will depend on thickness of hair, enough for repeated use. For best results always use fresh, new blades</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>Universal Unisex Razor Comb Home Hair Cut Scissor with 5 Extra Blades</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">17.49</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Save time and money with the double-sided Unisex Razor Comb hair cutting and trimming tool for the home hair cut.  Cut your hair as you comb it! It can be used to shape, style, shave, trim, thin and taper your hair.\n\nNo trip to the barber or hairstylist is needed for the best hair style and great appearances when you have this hair cutting and thinning razor comb around your house. The hair razor comb has two lengths on each side, used for short hair and long hair. It is simple to use, just a you would brush your hair, it will evenly trim and shape any style you want to create. Thinning your hair with these hair shears with help your hair breath and promote healthier hair locks and split ends. For use on both thin and thick hair cutting, trimming and styling.\n\nThe razor comb is ideal for unwanted facial hair and is a great option for both men and women. It can be used to thin beards and mustaches and can reach other places that are hard to reach. The home styling razor comb specializes in getting a close shave while cutting angles and blending a fade in your hair while you comb it. \n\nEasy and convenient to use at home, the razor comb features 2 edges and a regular comb on the other end. If the blades begin to dull, the included bonus razors will come in handy to replace and reuse with the razor comb. The replacement blades are standard double-sided razor blades so there is no worry to buy expensive specialized replacement cartridges. Always use a fresh razor blade for best results. \n\nRazor comb works best when hair is lightly wet. Once wet, comb first before using the cutting razor side. Use proper side of razor comb for your desired hair length, proceed to comb hair with razor, going slow to start.\n\nPlease Note, personal results will vary person to person due to different hair styles and textures.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\